    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We can fix this by testing the text width against the label width. If it overlaps, try removing a character and appending a `...`.  Repeat until the text width is less than the label width.  This can be implemented as a `string WidgetUtils.TruncateStringToWidth(string text, SpriteFont font, int maxWidth)` function.\n"
